is even the right word.

512
00:35:03,702 --> 00:35:05,728
You've never been
attracted to other women?

513
00:35:07,505 --> 00:35:08,564
Of course not.

514
00:35:08,807 --> 00:35:10,799
You don't check
anyone out at the beach?

515
00:35:11,109 --> 00:35:13,237
You see a girl on the
street in tight jeans?

516
00:35:13,311 --> 00:35:14,540
I check them out.

517
00:35:17,782 --> 00:35:19,080
I don't jump them.

518
00:35:20,485 --> 00:35:21,976
I don't even want to jump them.

519
00:35:27,325 --> 00:35:32,764
Your wife acted on every
single temptation she had,

520
00:35:32,998 --> 00:35:36,628
every single ugly,
stupid temptation.

521
00:35:38,703 --> 00:35:40,137
But she never left you.

522
00:35:41,039 --> 00:35:44,407
The one thing you know
for sure, through all of that,

523
00:35:45,777 --> 00:35:49,475
she was never even tempted
to walk away from you.

524
00:35:57,155 --> 00:35:58,680
She never stopped loving you.

525
00:36:25,717 --> 00:36:27,845
You know, I knew this couple.

526
00:36:31,523 --> 00:36:32,718
They had a child.

527
00:36:34,693 --> 00:36:38,323
They were happy
and building a life.

528
00:36:41,666 --> 00:36:48,630
One day, the husband found out
that the wife hadn't been honest.

529
00:36:51,843 --> 00:36:53,141
It broke their trust.

530
00:36:54,946 --> 00:37:01,580
And instead of working it out,
they let the deception fester.

531
00:37:03,354 --> 00:37:07,052
Eventually, the husband
moved out, moved away,

532
00:37:10,595 --> 00:37:11,595
barely sees his kid.

533
00:37:14,365 --> 00:37:16,732
I don't need any
more of your parables.

534
00:37:19,738 --> 00:37:22,367
You and your stories
are the reason I'm here.

535
00:37:24,809 --> 00:37:27,005
You're here because
you choose to be here.

536
00:37:38,256 --> 00:37:41,055
Was that even true? That story.

537
00:37:43,728 --> 00:37:44,728
No.

538
00:37:56,941 --> 00:37:58,170
It's done?

539
00:38:00,378 --> 00:38:04,076
Yes, the tumor
has been resected.

540
00:38:05,617 --> 00:38:07,017
Would you like to kiss me?

541
00:38:11,322 --> 00:38:12,790
Maybe a little.

542
00:38:15,326 --> 00:38:16,988
But I'm not going to.

543
00:38:18,563 --> 00:38:20,122
That's a very good sign.

544
00:39:00,972 --> 00:39:02,838
That's a very good sign.

545
00:39:25,730 --> 00:39:28,063
Measles kill.
Broken homes don't.

