00:39:30,201 --> 00:39:31,999
Go to a bar. Let off some steam.

547
00:39:33,137 --> 00:39:34,737
I'm going to the range.

548
00:39:37,508 --> 00:39:39,443
- You have your own gun?
- I have three.

549
00:39:40,211 --> 00:39:41,211
Can I come?

550
00:39:45,316 --> 00:39:47,148
- Are you gonna talk?
- No.

551
00:39:50,355 --> 00:39:51,755
You pay for your own ammo.

552
00:40:01,532 --> 00:40:03,524
- Hi, Shaun.
- Hello.

553
00:40:04,535 --> 00:40:05,833
No Lea?

554
00:40:05,904 --> 00:40:09,898
She's out drinking with friends.
Other friends. I'm her friend.

555
00:40:10,008 --> 00:40:12,910
But I didn't want to go. So
I'm watching Albert the fish.

556
00:40:13,444 --> 00:40:15,879
Okay. I brought some tests.

557
00:40:17,649 --> 00:40:19,982
- Where did I get my couch?
- What?

558
00:40:20,084 --> 00:40:21,518
It's a memory test.

559
00:40:21,586 --> 00:40:25,045
Hopkins verbal learning,
COWA, these are memory tests.

560
00:40:25,123 --> 00:40:27,149
Some of the
questions are harder.

