562
00:40:30,561 --> 00:40:31,859
Okay. Fine,

563
00:40:31,930 --> 00:40:35,264
you got your couch from the
bus you lived in with your brother.

564
00:40:36,634 --> 00:40:38,034
Who gave me my bookshelf?

565
00:40:38,803 --> 00:40:41,136
