566
00:40:41,572 --> 00:40:42,972
And my lamp?

567
00:40:46,544 --> 00:40:47,637
Do you know?

568
00:40:47,745 --> 00:40:49,737
A teacher. Shannon.

569
00:40:49,814 --> 00:40:54,149
No, that's wrong. Her name was
